        <item>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>School Resource Officer Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Omnibus Crime Control and Safe Streets Act of 1968 to reauthorize through FY2022 the Community Oriented Policing Services (COPS) program and modify it:</p> <ul> <li>to restore authority to make COPS grants for hiring and rehiring additional career law enforcement officers, and </li> <li>to specify that at least 30 percent of the amount made available for such grants must be used for school resource officers. </li> </ul>]]></text>
